name: citryl-CoA lyase
comment: The enzyme is a component of EC 4.1.3.6 {[citrate (pro-3S)-lyase]}and EC 2.3.3.8 [ATP citrate synthase]. Also acts on (3S)-citryl thioacyl-carrier protein.

orthologs.K01644: citrate lyase subunit beta / citryl-CoA lyase

references.title: Characterization of the isolated transferase subunit of citrate lyase as a CoA-Transferase. Evidence against a covalent enzyme-substrate intermediate.
Isolation of enzymically active fragments formed by limited proteolysis of ATP citrate lyase.
